{"type":null,"faqId":37075,"title":"手环连接手机，手机播放的歌曲为什么是外放的？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\r\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\r\n.p2{text-indent:0.14583333in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>当蓝牙耳机没有从腕带上取下时，手机播放歌曲是外放的。 <br>\n1、请确保您的手环与手机蓝牙连接正常；2、如果耳机没有从腕带上取出，手机播放歌曲是外放的；3、如果蓝牙耳机已从腕带拿取出，手机播放歌曲还是外放的话，请重启下手机和手环后重新连接，再取出蓝牙耳机确认是否可以正常收听；4、以上解决办法无效，请反馈给人工客服。</span></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2239","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750141000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":42,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,蓝牙音乐,音质低,媒体音频,耳机听音乐","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}